data.description: Welcome to your next investment opportunity! This charming cape code style home, nestled on a wooded lot in Winterville, is awaiting its transformation. Being sold AS-IS, it presents a perfect project for an investor or someone with a knack for renovation.    With a little TLC, this home has the potential to shine once again. Boasting 3 spacious bedrooms, including a coveted master suite on the main level, and an additional 2 bedrooms on the second level, theres plenty of space to customize to your liking.    Inside, youll find real hardwoods that add warmth and character to the space, creating a cozy atmosphere. Plus, enjoy the added bonus of a screened porch off the back of the home, perfect for enjoying the serene wooded surroundings.    Conveniently located close to shopping centers and grocery stores, everything you need is just a short drive away. Whether youre looking for your next flip project or a place to make your own, this home offers endless potential in a desirable location.    Dont miss out on this opportunity to turn this diamond in the rough into your dream home or a lucrative investment. Schedule a showing today and unlock the possibilities that await!
